<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <!-- This meta tag is the key to mobile responsiveness -->
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Pro Level Baseball</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: sans-serif; margin: 0; padding: 0; line-height: 1.6; }
        header { background: #333; color: #fff; padding: 1rem; text-align: center; }
        .container { padding: 20px; max-width: 800px; margin: auto; }
        
        /* Grid layout for drills - switches to 1 column on small screens */
        .grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr)); gap: 20px; }
        
        .card { border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; }
        footer { text-align: center; padding: 20px; background: #f4f4f4; margin-top: 20px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
    <h1>Pro Level Baseball</h1>
</header>

<div class="container">
    <h2>Welcome to Elite Training</h2>
    <p>Master your mechanics with our professional-grade drills.</p>
    
    <h3>Featured Drills</h3>
    <div class="grid">
        <div class="card">
            <h4>Hitting Mechanics</h4>
            <p>Perfect your swing path with these fundamental drills.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <h4>Pitching Velocity</h4>
            <p>Unlock more power with our specialized arm-care program.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <h4>Fielding Basics</h4>
            <p>Work on footwork and glove transitions.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<footer>
    <p>&copy; 2026 Pro Level Baseball</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>

